<br>
I put the 49th (24pt) thorns on the tank, buffed him with Skin Like Nature and Chloroplast.  Assuming he has self buffs to level.  The Widowmistress died really easily; only had to G.Heal the ranger two times.  Other then Ensnaring the mob, cast no offensive spells on her.  She dropped the Stiletto of Bloodclaw, which his rogue twink will get <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START 8) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/glasses.gif ALT="8)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> .<br>
<br>
Wow 600 pts of healing and chloroplast on a moderately equipped 36 ranger, makes him stronger than a post 50 mage and post 50 warrior for damage output?<br>
