<br>
New additions:<br>
Goblin fort in Warsliks woods is easy to solo (grachnist the destroyer drops iksar scaled gloves and goblin shrunken earing as a rare).  Lots of goblins but above 50 they do not agro, some may heal but that is about it.  51 earth pet is enough.<br>
<br>
Sarnak Fort in Lake Of Ill Omen, many sarnaks do not agro.  Sarnaks drop Sarnak emblazaned tobard, sarnak earing of station, sarnak ceremonial dagger, and some other decent stuff.  Chancellor drops Jade Chokidai Prod.  He is 40 and has a pet.  Best is to nuke the pet with your best summons spell and send your pet in, it will level the doggy real fast and then Chancellor is no problem.<br>
